    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Yuba City, California",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "RESEARCH",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Rebulet 6-5-50.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Subject was located 6-13-50 residing at [REDACTED] San Jose, California. He was interviewed by SA [REDACTED] of this Office, who carefully explained the jurisdiction of the FBI to him and questioned him relative to any information he might have which would be of interest to this Bureau.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] had nothing to add to his previous story as submitted by letter to the Bureau on 4-9-50. He was advised that any information relative to \"flying saucers\" did not come within the jurisdiction of this Bureau and that he could communicate such information to the Secretary of the Air Force, National Defense Building, The Pentagon, Washington 25, D. C.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "For the further information of the Bureau, Mr. [REDACTED], Mr. [REDACTED] was contacted in an effort to locate Mr. [REDACTED]. Mr. [REDACTED] described [REDACTED] as being \"odd\" but would not elaborate on this statement.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "It was also ascertained from [REDACTED], San Jose, California, through whom [REDACTED] was located, that [REDACTED] was given to weird imaginings. Mr. [REDACTED] stated that he would not exactly describe [REDACTED] as being insane but stated that he was getting along in years and was prone to exaggerate on queer imaginings.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "It was the observation of the interviewing agent that Mr. [REDACTED] is abnormal mentally.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
